  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nIf User receives a message in 1-1 chat that is displayed in the Activity Center, but opens it from the public chat, then that chat will be displayed in both the Activity Center and the Home screen after opening.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nOnce opened, chat isn't displayed in the Activity Center, no matter what screen it was opened from.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/116097567-8cb11a00-a6aa-11eb-9700-3bb7f427a3c3.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\nUser A:\r\n- Join public chat\r\n- Send a message\r\n- Start 1-1 chat with User B\r\n- Send a message\r\nUser B:\r\n- Check that 1-1 chat with User A appeared in the Activity Center (don't open it)\r\n- Join the same public chat\r\n- Tap User's A username to open his profile\r\n- Tap `Chat` to start 1-1\r\n- Send a message\r\n- Navigate to the Activity Center to check that the 1-1 is still displayed in the Activity Center\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Nightly 26/04\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS",
